%%spark
val x1 = spark.read.parquet("/output6/*")
x1.createOrReplaceTempView("outputFinal")
display(spark.sql("select * from outputFinal order by tpepPickupDateTime desc"))

%%spark
import spark.sqlContext.implicits._
import org.apache.spark.sql.functions._
var df2 = spark.sql("select *, " +
    "cast('2022-04-10T10:56:25.000+0000' as TIMESTAMP) as data_out1," +
    "cast('2022-04-10T10:56:25.000+0000' as TIMESTAMP) as data_out from outputFinal order by tpepPickupDateTime desc limit 1"
    )
df2=df2.drop(df2("vendorID")).drop(df2("tpepDropoffDateTime")).drop(df2("tpepPickupDateTime")).withColumn("vendorID",lit("pombo")).withColumn("tpepPickupDateTime",col("data_out1")).withColumn("tpepDropoffDateTime",col("data_out")).drop(df2("data_out")).drop(df2("data_out1"))
df2= df2.select(df2("vendorID")
                ,df2("tpepPickupDateTime")
                ,df2("tpepDropoffDateTime"),
                df2("passengerCount")
                ,df2("tripDistance")
                ,df2("puLocationId")
                ,df2("doLocationId")
                ,df2("startLon")
                ,df2("startLat")
                ,df2("endLon")
                ,df2("endLat")
                ,df2("rateCodeId")
                ,df2("storeAndFwdFlag")
                ,df2("paymentType")
                ,df2("fareAmount"))
display(df2)
